{
  "stem": "734.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was not enough food to survive and work that hard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they made this agreement with the SS administration, apparently, for them to supplement food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And something like twice a week, they would bring in-- they would allow certain rations to all the special productive workers, that is.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever, whoever they picked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every department would get so many.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They drew a list as to how many each department, like lathe operators, planer operators, sheet metal workers would get such and such.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a variety.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bread, the real bread that the Germans ate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not the camp bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You realize that the bread in camp had a lot of sawdust?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A lot, a lot of sawdust.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You could see it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, you took a piece of bread and you crumpled it in your hands and it almost as much sawdust as anything else had in it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- so they had this agreement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was like, soup, skim milk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Skim milk for the people who were spraying the fuselages, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know why they were-- they worried about the lungs of the sprayers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, people were dying left and ride, being killed and shot, and died of all kinds of diseases.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And suddenly, these guys worry about-- about lungs of a man who sprays the fuselage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's just so stupid, I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was chosen, recommended by this overseer from the planers, to-- to take care of the food problem.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I-- that is to-- because this food would have to be brought in from the Messerschmidt warehouse, which was right outside, maybe half a mile away from the plant, Sankt Georgen, in Austria.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
